<h2 id="stopping-local-services" class="group scroll-mt-24">Stopping local services<a href="#stopping-local-services" aria-hidden="true" class="ml-2 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition"><span aria-hidden="true">#</span></a></h2>
